const params = ctx.stateController.getStateParams(); // console.log("DetailParams=>", params) const typeMachine = ['ClearSkyClient', 'MicroTRACKClient', 'JDeereClient', 'JCBClient', 'ScaniaClient', 'VolvoClient', 'KomatsuClient', 'SMART_ONE_C' ] const dictionaryTypeMachine = { 'ClearSkyClient': "ClearSky", 'MicroTRACKClient': "MicroTRACK", 'JDeereClient': "JDeere", 'JCBClient': 'JCB', 'ScaniaClient': "Scania", "VolvoClient":"Volvo", KomatsuClient:"Komatsu", 'SMART_ONE_C': "SMARTONE C", } const isMachine = typeMachine.includes(data[0]['DataOrigin']); // console.log("data[0]",data[0]) const isDevice = data[0]['entityType'] === 'DEVICE'; const isDeviceWithType = isDevice && typeMachine.includes( data[0]['DataOrigin']); // console.log("TypeDevice=>", data) ///--- General views ---/// const generalDashboardStates = { ClearSkyClient: 'detail_default_general', 'JCBClient' : 'detail_default_general', 'MicroTRACKClient': 'detail_default_general', 'JDeereClient': 'detail_default_general', 'ScaniaClient': 'detail_default_general', 'VolvoClient':'detail_default_general', 'KomatsuClient': 'detail_default_general', 'SMART_ONE_C': 'detail_default_general', } ///--- Utilization views ---/// const utilizationDashboardStates = { ClearSkyClient: 'detail_default_monitoring', 'JCBClient' : 'detail_default_monitoring', 'MicroTRACKClient': 'detail_default_monitoring', 'JDeereClient': 'detail_default_monitoring', 'ScaniaClient': 'detail_default_monitoring', 'VolvoClient':'detail_default_monitoring', 'KomatsuClient': 'detail_default_monitoring', 'SMART_ONE_C': 'detail_default_monitoring', } ///--- Alarm Views ---/// const alarmsDashboardStates = { ClearSkyClient: 'detail_default_alarms', 'JCBClient' : 'detail_default_alarms', 'MicroTRACKClient': 'detail_default_alarms', 'JDeereClient': 'detail_default_alarms', 'ScaniaClient': 'detail_default_alarms', 'VolvoClient':'detail_default_alarms', 'KomatsuClient': 'detail_default_alarms', 'SMART_ONE_C': 'detail_default_alarms', } let generalStateId = '', utilizationStateId = '', historyStateId = '', alarmStateId = ''; if (isMachine && !isDevice) { generalStateId = generalDashboardStates[data[0]['DataOrigin']] utilizationStateId = utilizationDashboardStates[data[0][ 'type' ]] alarmStateId = alarmsDashboardStates[data[0]['DataOrigin']] } if (!isMachine && isDevice) { generalStateId = 'detail_default_general' utilizationStateId = 'detail_default_monitoring' alarmStateId = 'detail_default_alarms' } if (!isMachine && isDeviceWithType) { generalStateId = generalDashboardStates[data[0][ 'DataOrigin' ]] utilizationStateId = utilizationDashboardStates[data[0][ 'DataOrigin' ]] alarmStateId = alarmsDashboardStates[data[0][ 'DataOrigin' ]] } const indexsTabs = { general: 0, utilization: 1, alarms: 2, history: 3 } let indextTab = 0 if (params.showDescriptionAsset) { indextTab = indexsTabs[params.showDescriptionAsset.view] } // console.log("DataMon=>", isMachine, generalStateId, // utilizationStateId, historyStateId, alarmStateId) const templateOneMachine = `
General
Monitoreo
Alarmas
` const templateGrid = `
Select device
` return (isMachine || isDevice) ? templateOneMachine : templateGrid
